window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>She yearned for him.</p> <p>Nyla Mullaney couldn't shake her want for a man she knew could never be hers.</p> <p>He desired her.</p> <p>Asan Chamberlain sought peace and found it in a woman who he should've been avoiding at all costs.</p> <p>They formed a bond that had them treading in forbidden waters with no desire to escape. Nyla and Asan were never meant to be, history said so, but fate had other plans.</p> <p>Contains mature themes.</p>"; 
